<TEXT>
<P>
   The Seattle Post-Intelligencer plans to move the following
stories for clients of the NYTimes News Service for editions of
Monday, Sept. 9 and thereafter. If you have any questions, please
call Mary Downes on the national-foreign desk at (206) 448-8158.
</P>
<P>
   BOEING-EMPLOYMENT (Seattle) _ Developments in Boeing employment
in the Puget Sound region and in Wichita, Kan. Exclusive.
