Golden State Forwards Danny Fortson and Adam Keefe. Utah Forward
Donyell Marshall, center Bruno Sundov. Boston Guard Robert Pack,
center John ``Hot Rod'' Williams, Utah's first-round pick in 2001,
cash.
</P>
