<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-17 01:55 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4305 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r a BC-DNC-PROTESTS-2TAKES-L     08-17 0896
