   MOVIE-REVIEW-CELL _ Art direction-heavy serial killer movie with
Jennifer Lopez entering the mind of the murderer. Visually
stunning, narratively impaired. Grade: C-. (StMurray, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 17.
</P>
<P>
   MOVIE-REVIEW-DEMENTED _ ``Cecil B. Demented.'' John Waters film
with Melanie Griffith as movie star kidnapped by underground
filmmakers. Grade: C-. (Ringel, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 15.
</P>
<P>
   MOVIE-REVIEW-GIRL _ ``The Girl on the Bridge.'' From the
director of ``Monsieur Hire.'' And not nearly as good. Grade: C+.
(Ringel, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 12.
</P>
<P>
   MOVIE-REVIEW-GODZILLA _ ``Godzilla 2000.'' It's back in the
hands of the Japanese and stars a guy in a gojira suit. Grade: B.
(BLongino, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 13.
</P>
<P>
   MOVIE-REVIEW-KINGS _ ``The Original Kings of Comedy.'' Black
stand-up comics in performance film. Grade: A-. (StMurray, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   MOVIE-REVIEW-PSYCHO _ ``Psycho Beach Party.'' We saw this at
Sundance. It's not really very good. Grade: C+. (StMurray, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 13.
</P>
<P>
   MOVIE-REVIEW-SAVING _ ``Saving Grace.'' with Brenda Blethyn in
quirky comedy as widow who needs cash to survive and so she starts
growing marijuana. Grade: B-. (StMurray, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 13.
</P>
