   CONSULTANT-BOOM-HARVARD-BUSINESS-PUBLISHING _ The terms are used
loosely: independent contractor, contract employee, consultant. But
the phenomenon they refer to _ people who put in a substantial
number of hours at a company but are not legally employees of the
