<P>
   ``IN GRAND SLAM SUMMER, TIGER (RE)TAILS.'' Tiger Woods has
already printed his name in golf's record books; his British Open
victory made him the youngest player to complete golf's career
Grand Slam. His impact on fashion, however, and the aesthetic of
his namesake Nike Golf apparel line are just starting to break out
from behind his black-and-red-on-Sundays signature. A report.
(slugged: BC-TIGER-WOODS-RETAIL-FAIRCHILD-NYTSF)
