 &HT;    Here, some treats for your body to beat the summer heat.
 &HT;    
 &HT;    HEAD FOR THE ORIENT
 &HT;    
 &HT;    Classic fragrances are back, and what more luxurious way to wear
them than in your hair? Not only does Guerlain's limited-edition
Shalimar Perfumed Beautifying Hair Gel leave a whisper of the
mysterious scent on your pillow, but the bottle's also something to
behold. Available at all Guerlain boutiques or at Guerlain Boutique
by Mail, (800) 822-8820.
 &HT;    
 &HT;    METAL HEAD
 &HT;    
 &HT;    Candy-colored nails _ a summertime favorite _ have been given a
sexy update with subtle flashes of metal. The result? Perennial
shades that constantly surprise. From Tony &AMP; Tina Vibrational
Remedies, try Nail Paint in Kundalini, Visualize and Mystic.
Available at www.tonytina.com.
 &HT;    
 &HT;    VICTORIA'S OTHER SECRET
 &HT;    
 &HT;    Top off the little something special from Victoria's Secret with
a swipe of the lingerie giant's new high-shine lipstick,
Reflections. Can't choose from the array of 25 shades in five color
families? Then reach for the line's chic Pure Reflections
Mini-Lipstick Sampler for a taste of the most dazzling shades.
