<P>
   CVN-CONVENTION-RDP (Los Angeles) _ At last, Vice President Al
Gore makes his debut as the Democratic presidential nominee. Gore
addresses the Democratic National Convention in what aides say will
be an hour-long speech that is rich in details about his policy
