that is home to the Ritz Hotel, several haute couture boutiques and
some of the world's most expensive jewelry shops, ``Place Vendome''
provides a perfect setting for Catherine Deneuve, herself one of
the French cinema's most precious gems. Reviewed by David Kehr.
</P>
<P>
   STEAL-FILM-REVIEW (Undated) _ ``Steal This Movie!,'' Robert
Greenwald's likable but muddled screen biography of the charismatic
Yippie activist Abbie Hoffman. With Vincent D'Onofrio, Janeane
Garofalo, Jeanne Tripplehorn, Kevin Pollak, Kevin Corrigan, Donal
Logue, Troy Garrity. Reviewed by Stephen Holden.
