<P>
   Getting By Air There From The New York Area
</P>
<P>
   Continental, (800) 525-0280, has four daily nonstop flights from
Newark Airport, starting at $533 round trip with a 21-day advance
purchase and a Saturday stay-over. The 14-day advance purchase fare
is $905 round trip. Last-minute flights cost up to $1,065 one way.
</P>
<P>
   American, (800) 433-7300, has one daily nonstop flight from
Kennedy Airport, starting at $528 round trip with a 21-day advance
purchase and a Saturday stay-over. The 14-day advance purchase fare
ranges from $900 to $962. The last-minute fare costs up to $2,326,
round trip.
</P>
<P>
   Delta, (800) 221-1212, also has one daily nonstop flight from
Kennedy, with comparable fares; as does United, (800) 241-6522,
with round-trip fares beginning at $780 with a 21-day advance
purchase and a Saturday stay-over.
