   BOTTOM
</P>
<P>
   DEM-SPEECH-NYT _ A look at the convention speech itself and how
Al Gore arrived at the words and themes. By Melinda Henneberger.
</P>
<P>
   With photo.
</P>
<P>
   (Scheduled to move by 9 p.m. ET in ``p'' news file.)
</P>
<P>
   NY-CHARTER-SCHOOL (Undated) _ When Gov. George Pataki visited
the newly opened New Covenant charter school in Albany last fall,
he proclaimed it a model of the kind of educational change he was
trying to create. In the months following the visit, however, New
Covenant descended into apparent chaos, with fourth-graders scoring
among the lowest in the state on standardized tests, the for-profit
company overseeing the school resigning and two principals
quitting. How things went so wrong so quickly at New Covenant is a
cautionary tale for entrepreneurs, education reformers and
politicians who are tempted by the vaunted promise of charter
schools. By Edward Wyatt.
</P>
<P>
   (Scheduled to move by 8 p.m. ET in ``a'' news file.)
</P>
