<P>
   __ Speculation about how News Corp's pending $3.5 billion
purchase of Chris-Craft TV stations will affect local sports
coverage. For example, with Fox taking control of both Channel 11
and 13, Dodgers over-the-air coverage could switch from KTLA
Channel 5 when the current contract runs out. The sale probably
won't go down until middle of next year. &QL;
