<DOCNO> NYT20000817.0476 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-17 22:35 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5125 &Cx1f; tad-z
b p BC-CVN-MAIN18-COX     08-17 0791
